---

<MainLayout
  title="TPO Roofing Installation in Temple, Killeen & Central Texas | Lone Ranger Roofing"
  description="Lone Ranger Roofing installs TPO roofing systems for commercial properties across Temple, Killeen, and Central Texas. Energy-efficient, heat-welded, built for Texas flat roofs. Free commercial estimate."
  darkHero={true}
>

  <!-- ===================== HERO ===================== -->
  <section class="relative min-h-[65vh] flex items-center bg-brand-900 overflow-hidden -mt-28">
    <div class="absolute inset-0">
      <img
        src="/tpo1.webp"
        alt="Commercial TPO roofing installation — Temple and Killeen TX"
        class="w-full h-full object-cover"
      />
      <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-r from-brand-900 via-brand-900/85 to-brand-900/30"></div>
    </div>

    <div class="relative z-10 container mx-auto px-4 py-28">
      <div class="max-w-2xl">
        <p class="text-gold-400 font-bold text-sm uppercase tracking-widest mb-4">Commercial Roofing &rsaquo; TPO Roofing</p>
        <h1 class="text-4xl sm:text-5xl lg:text-6xl font-black text-white leading-tight mb-6">
          TPO Roofing for Commercial Properties in Temple, Killeen &amp; Central Texas
        </h1>
        <p class="text-xl text-gray-200 leading-relaxed mb-8">
          The most cost-effective flat roofing system for Texas heat. Minimal disruption to your operations.
        </p>
        <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4">
          <a href="/contact" class="bg-accent-600 hover:bg-accent-700 text-white font-black px-8 py-4 rounded-lg text-sm uppercase tracking-wide transition-colors text-center shadow-lg">
            Get a Free Commercial Estimate
          </a>
          <a href="tel:+12543001413" class="border-2 border-white/50 hover:border-white text-white font-bold px-8 py-4 rounded-lg text-sm uppercase tracking-wide transition-colors text-center hover:bg-white/10">
            Call (254) 300-1413
          </a>
        </div>

        <!-- Trust bar -->
        <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-x-6 gap-y-3 mt-10">
          {[
            'Heat-Welded Seams',
            'Energy-Efficient White Membrane',
            'Material + Labor Warranty',
          ].map(t => (
            <div class="flex items-center gap-2 text-gray-300 text-sm">
              <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-gold-400 flex-shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"/>
              </svg>
              {t}
            </div>
          ))}
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ===================== WHAT IS TPO ===================== -->
  <section class="py-20 bg-white overflow-hidden">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
      <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center max-w-6xl mx-auto">

        <!-- Photo side -->
        <div class="relative order-2 lg:order-1">
          <img
            src="/tpo2.webp"
            alt="TPO roofing membrane installation on a commercial flat roof — Central Texas"
            class="w-full h-[480px] object-cover rounded-2xl shadow-xl"
          />
          <div class="absolute bottom-6 right-6 bg-brand-900 text-white rounded-xl p-5 max-w-[230px] shadow-xl border border-white/10">
            <p class="text-gold-400 font-bold text-xs uppercase tracking-widest mb-3">TPO Is the Right Call If Your Property Has:</p>
            <ul class="space-y-1.5">
              {[
                'A flat or low-slope roof',
                'High summer cooling costs',
                "An aging membrane that's leaking or failing",
                'A tight project timeline with minimal disruption needed',
                'A budget that needs to perform long-term',
              ].map(item => (
                <li class="flex items-start gap-2 text-brand-200 text-xs leading-snug">
                  <svg class="w-3 h-3 text-accent-600 flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                    <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"/>
                  </svg>
                  {item}
                </li>
              ))}
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Text side -->
        <div class="order-1 lg:order-2">
          <p class="text-accent-600 font-bold text-sm uppercase tracking-widest mb-3">What Is TPO Roofing</p>
          <h2 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-black text-brand-900 mb-6">
            What Is TPO Roofing and Why Do Commercial Properties in Central Texas Choose It?
          </h2>
          <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed mb-5">
            TPO — Thermoplastic Polyolefin — is a single-ply roofing membrane designed specifically for flat and low-slope commercial roofs. It's one of the most widely used commercial roofing systems in Texas for good reason: it reflects solar heat instead of absorbing it, handles UV exposure and punctures better than older membrane systems, and installs efficiently with minimal disruption to the businesses operating below.
          </p>
          <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
            For property owners and managers in Temple, Killeen, Belton, Waco, and throughout the DFW area dealing with 100-degree summers and unpredictable storm seasons, TPO is a practical, proven solution that protects the building and reduces energy costs for the life of the roof.
          </p>
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ===================== WHY TPO ===================== -->
  <section class="py-20 bg-gray-50">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4 max-w-6xl">

      <div class="flex flex-col lg:flex-row gap-10 items-center mb-14">
        <div class="lg:w-1/2">
          <p class="text-accent-600 font-bold text-sm uppercase tracking-widest mb-3">TPO vs. Other Systems</p>
          <h2 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-black text-brand-900 mb-4">
            TPO vs. Other Commercial Roofing Systems
          </h2>
          <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
            Property managers in Central Texas have options when it comes to flat roofing. Here's where TPO stands out.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="lg:w-1/2 grid grid-cols-2 gap-3">
          <img src="/tpo3.webp" alt="TPO commercial roofing — Temple TX" class="w-full h-40 object-cover rounded-xl shadow-md" />
          <img src="/tpo4.webp" alt="Flat roof membrane installation — Central Texas" class="w-full h-40 object-cover rounded-xl shadow-md mt-6" />
        </div>
      </div>

